{"tid":233975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳美齡：覺得自己不會做教育局長","createTime":"2017-05-08T02:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T02:37:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3bc09d8577ac7a10f3ba9722ca4f3a9260f23a","tid":233975,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170508/s00001/f86b84b2d89784407bfc1dcd2d34c583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2Ff86b84b2d89784407bfc1dcd2d34c583.jpg&h=1ddb0433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n候任特首林鄭月娥正籌組下屆政府班子，有報道指持史丹福大學教育博士學位的前歌手陳美齡是教育局長人選之一。陳美齡今早在商台節目承認，曾多次與林太交流教育議題，亦被問及「對香港是否很有感情」，對於會否出任教育局長，她則說「假設性問題不回答」。<br />\n<br />\n對於被傳教育局長人選之一，陳美齡表示，當時有記者問及有關事宜，她回應「no commemts（不評論），就令人認為「可能是又可能不是」，她說她姊姊都跟她說若答不是「咪冇咩事囉」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否有更清晰說法，陳美齡則說「有朋友教我，假設性問題不回答」，但表示若林太考慮推薦她出任教育局長，亦是一個鼓勵，顯示林太對其提議有興趣。主持人追問林鄭月娥在會面中有否提過此說法，陳重申「假設性問題不回答」，並說「我想我不會答」。<br />\n<br />\n陳美齡表示，林鄭月娥當選後曾多次跟她交流教育議題，但並非林太主動邀請，只是「大家的朋友想大家見面」，亦不是單獨會面，她指林太對其建議很有興趣。被問到林太有否邀請她留港為教育做多些事，陳則說「她問我對香港是否很有感情」。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，林太對教師待遇問題最有興趣，因現時待遇不平均，如合約制、副教師等問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳其後在節目中又表示「覺得自己不會做教育局長」，被問到是否代表不會做全職公務員，而是以顧問形式服務，她則說自己是白紙一張，現在只是開始，但大家討論是非常好的事。她又說，「不是你自己想做什麼就什麼，人家找你才可以做」，並指若留港全職工作，日本那邊的工作會有困難，亦說需視乎崗位是否適合自己。"},{"pid":"8956bc94f91a070f48a734cced0c382fbfa989a8","tid":233975,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170508/s00001/1494205810460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2F1494205810460&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=788817b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170508%2Fs00001%2F1494205810460&h=2136d392\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170508/s00001/1494205810460</a>"},{"pid":"177e3e809132bcf59993b4a4b337794de81deb94","tid":233975,"uid":29011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1V8895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1V8895.jpg&h=c4202399&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"465750cabb7752bb0c43db50315310267cf30daf","tid":233975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"淨話有聽， 好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係邊聽邊喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要搵方法聽吓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳美齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af79a15df5b57c42ff72d0559783abc9ce5ed8cc","tid":233975,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83287421bdd0acf5bc2fc8eb1df7e98d30068fe8","tid":233975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨話有聽， 好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係邊聽邊喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要搵方法聽吓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳美齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊今朝 881既在情朗的一天出發"},{"pid":"5ee60ceeec48a0096f5d96b8ffb18377f9869acf","tid":233975,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:37:32.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c1613c59a8ac8f409f13ba053f5177f1fdacab3d","tid":